title: Surfing Is Everything: Rip Curl Groms - Costa Rica
description:
Rip Curl upstarts Wyatt McHale (Oahu, 13), Crosby Colapinto (San Clemente, 13), & Jett Schilling (San Clemente, 11), escape south to explore the Costa Rican coastline. These groms ooze froth whether in the lineup or playing games on the beach, which illustrates why Surfing Is Everything to them.

Filmed & Edited by: Justin Jung

Track: Rootshine Revival
Artist: The Polish Ambassador

Track: Chopper
Artist: Masonic
